far-left Refounded Communist Party to support his budget cuts in
parliament.
</P>
<P>
Hollande said that the French Socialist Party hopes that a
solution will be found to this crisis by the Italians, so that
Italy can maintain its choice to join the European single currency
by January 1999, and to fight unemployment and social inequality.
</P>
<P>
"All should be done to avoid that the Italian right allied
with the extreme-right come to power," said the spokesman.
</P>
</TEXT>
