<HEADLINE> Zambia Unable to Meet All Needs from Refugees </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, October 9 (Xinhua) -- Zambia said today that it cannot
meet all the needs from the refugees living in the country
because its economy is already constrained.
</P>
