the building, where a meeting attended by the junta leader Major
Johnny Koroma was originally scheduled.
</P>
<P>
The venue of the meeting was changed at the last minute, the
report said.
</P>
<P>
A senior junta officer even declared after the ECOMOG attack
that the situation between Nigeria and Sierra Leone "has resulted
into a state of war".
</P>
<P>
