<HEADLINE> Special Education Meeting Held in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 10 (Xinhua) -- China's fourth annual meeting
on special education for deaf-mute and mentally retarded children
was held today in Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
