<HEADLINE> Senior Army Officer Meets Italian Defense Minister </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Fu Quanyou, member of China's
Central Military Commission, met with Italian Defense Minister
Beniamino Andreatta, and his party here today.
</P>
<P>
Fu, also chief of the general staff of the Chinese People's
Liberation Army, cited an ancient Chinese saying "seeing is
believing", noting Andreatta's visit has provided him with a good
opportunity to learn more about China.
</P>
<P>
This is of great significance for the promotion of the friendly
co-operation between the two countries and their armed forces, Fu
said.
</P>
<P>
Andreatta and his party arrived in Beijing Wednesday at the
invitation of China's Vice-Chairman of the Central Military
Commission Chi Haotian, who also serves as a State Councillor and
Minister of National Defense. 
</P>
