<HEADLINE> Temple's 1,400th Anniversary Celebrated in Eastern China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Monks from China, Japan and
the Republic of Korea gathered Wednesday to celebrate the 1,400th
anniversary of Guoqing Temple in Tiantai Mountains, Zhejiang
Province.
</P>
