<HEADLINE> World Cup Football Tables (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, October 10 (Xinhua) -- Following are the World Cup group
tables before this weekend's qualifying matches (tabulate under
played, won, drawn, goals for, against, points):
</P>
<P>
South America:
</P>
<P>
Argentina 14  8  4  2  22  12 28
