<P>
VIENNA, October 9 (Xinhua) -- American Todd Martin cracked
sixth-seeded Thomas Muster of Austria 6-4, 3-6, 6-4 Thursday to
reach the quarter-finals in the CA Trophy ATP Tour event.
</P>
